title: Eames Style Plywood Coffee Table
body: The Molded Plywood Coffee Table is a product of their signature molded plywood shaping technology in 1946. Charles Eames had ideas about making a better world and this table is the result of his good craftsmanship. It has been more than seven decades since this design was introduced yet it still catches the attention of anyone up to this generation. A remarkable masterpiece that embodies versatility and simplicity.
